    Lottie is a mobile library for Android and iOS that parses Adobe After Effects animations exported as json with Bodymovin and renders them natively on mobile!

    IoT Lab at KIIT is a group of committed students who work under the guidance of a group of capable and supportive teachers who guide us through each phase and stage. IoT Lab is a research forum that examines the possibilities of crowd sourcing and the Internet of Things for trans disciplinary research and initiatives that involve greater end-user participation. We currently have a number of successful goods and prototypes. We also provide web development and app development services.
